Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Murder of Lord Mountbatten
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040byhv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Sep 1979
Murder of Lord Mountbatten prompts need for clearer understanding of the Irish troubles among US voters. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less